body_html: @mrry fyi, I had to move saved_model deps from tf_cc_ops.cmake to tf_core_cpu.cmake to fix the windows cmake build. I added saved_model support to the C API in this set of changes, and it's closer to core anyway despite being under cc/.

body: @mrry fyi, I had to move saved_model deps from `tf_cc_ops.cmake` to `tf_core_cpu.cmake` to fix the windows cmake build. I added saved_model support to the C API in this set of changes, and it's closer to core anyway despite being under `cc/`.
